*'''獵戶座OB1b''' – 構成著名的[[獵戶腰帶|獵戶腰帶]][[星群|星群]]最亮的三顆星[[参宿一|獵戶座ζ]] (Alnitak)、 [[参宿二|獵戶座ε]] (Alnilam)、和[[参宿三|獵戶座δ]] (Mintaka)，還有一些其他的小星。這些恆星的平均年齡為800萬年，將來可能會分成3個群<ref name="WARREN1">{{cite journal 
    | title=A photometric study of the Orion OB 1 association. I - Observational data.
    | author=Warren, W. H., Jr.; Hesser, J. E.
    | journal=Astrophysical Journal Supplement Series, vol. 34, June 1977, p. 115-206
    | volume=34
    | pages=115–206
    | bibcode=1977ApJS...34..115W
    | format=PDF
    | doi=10.1086/190446|date=June 1977}}</ref><ref name="WARREN2">{{cite journal 
    | title=A photometric study of the Orion OB 1 association. III - Subgroup analyses
